# CC-Plugin TODO

## 架構重構藍圖 (Architecture Refactoring Roadmap)

依 [`plans/roadmap.md`](plans/roadmap.md) 拆分為四個漸進式階段：

- `Phase 1` — 建立單一 store 連線與設定純淨化 (30% 進度)
    - [ ] [plans/feat-single-state-store.md](plans/feat-single-state-store.md) — 單一 `StateStore` 連線，移除 `viper` 直接依賴
    - [ ] [plans/feat-config-externalization.md](plans/feat-config-externalization.md) — 硬編碼預設值移至 `default_settings.json`
    - [ ] [plans/feat-resource-leak-fix.md](plans/feat-resource-leak-fix.md) — 修復 `defer resp.Body.Close()` 於迴圈內的資源洩漏
- `Phase 2` — 消除重複代碼與服務層初步抽取 (55% 進度)
    - [ ] [plans/feat-reader-deduplication.md](plans/feat-reader-deduplication.md) — 合併 `gbrain` 與 `claudemem` 重複的讀取邏輯
    - [ ] [plans/feat-utility-extraction.md](plans/feat-utility-extraction.md) — `ExpandPath` 與 `temp_dir` 收斂至 `pkg/utils/`
- `Phase 3` — 建立核心服務層與介面抽離 (80% 進度)
    - [ ] [plans/feat-service-layer-extraction.md](plans/feat-service-layer-extraction.md) — 業務邏輯自 `cmd/` 移至 `internal/service/` 並定義介面
    - [ ] [plans/feat-static-registry.md](plans/feat-static-registry.md) — `Reader`/`Writer` 靜態註冊表
    - [ ] [plans/feat-structured-logging.md](plans/feat-structured-logging.md) — `fmt.Printf` 遷移至 `log/slog`
- `Phase 4` — 規範檔案更名與整合驗證 (100% 進度)
    - [ ] [plans/feat-skill-md-renaming.md](plans/feat-skill-md-renaming.md) — `anti-sabotage.md` 重命名為 `SKILL.md` 並補 frontmatter
    - [ ] [plans/feat-topology-extraction.md](plans/feat-topology-extraction.md) — `model/topology` 遷移至 `pkg/topology` 並新增 `cmd/topology` CLI

